title.en: Welcome to my Sonolus Ping Pong Game! :)

description.en:
Thank you so much for trying my simple ping pong game!

This unfinished game, is actually my very first "big" coding project, and so far it has been pretty cool to make!

However, it's still a huge work in progress, and a bunch of bugs are likely going to occur and also its kinda bad.
If you want to report bugs or request (reasonable) new features, feel free to contact me in the Sonolus Discord server or at the GitHub repo: https://github.com/patrickv0220/Sonolus-Ping-Pong-Game.

Current most important issues:
 - Skins from other engines are unlikely to work.

Have fun while playing!
